{"tid":1562193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部駐港特派員：各界應喊停暴力維護法治","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:24:21.000Z","uid":147956,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ef19ad03be04df81321df9cce53f0492339866","tid":1562193,"uid":147956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPVaaBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPVaaBP.jpg&h=e8fcc930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】外交部駐港特派員公署特派員謝鋒表示，香港一些極端勢力不斷將暴力升級，公然挑戰國家主權和一國兩制原則底線，影響香港市民生活和發展，呼籲各界站出來，叫停暴力及維護法治。<br />\n<br />\n謝鋒又表示，香港應該放下爭拗，抓緊一帶一路、粵港澳大灣區的發展機遇，才能拓展離岸貿易服務的空間，鞏固香港國際金融中心的地位。"},{"pid":"703062c76ab4db59cb48cb5f64886dacd43cb408","tid":1562193,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"281fdf72af20607dd3b4a70a49de803ab4880c36","tid":1562193,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:22:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ff540c2c68efb79a1502dead7d2c9fd42ec65534","tid":1562193,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:24:21.000Z","msg":"無人想要你個大灣區<br />\n係你一廂情願 懂唔撚懂呀共狗"}]}